651
00:41:33,052 --> 00:41:35,510
Besides, is it really appropriate to give a like for that?

652
00:41:35,510 --> 00:41:37,600
It doesn't matter to me.

653
00:41:39,176 --> 00:41:41,411
You didn't give me a like either.

654
00:41:41,411 --> 00:41:43,970
When I saw that, over ten hours had passed too.

655
00:41:43,970 --> 00:41:46,820
When you posted it, I was in the hospital.

656
00:41:47,320 --> 00:41:49,120
Fine.

657
00:41:50,820 --> 00:41:54,540
Well... Are we good?

